c $7D8C Soldier pattern 6: patrol (group B) + slow vertical drift
N $7D8C #R$8164 (synchronized left-right patrol, group B) plus the same slow vertical drift as pattern 4.
C $7D8F,3 BC = $0800 (slow drift rate)
