C $8A70,3 DI; select bank 0
C $8A73,5 Restore bank 0 paging
c $8A7A Run paged-bank routine, wait ~3 frames polling $C003
N $8A7A Drives the bank-1 vector table (init/step/finish) for a fixed 768-frame duration.
