C $9028,11 HL = screen address from soldier X
C $9033,7 Bit1 of X: E = $80 (sprite half)
C $903A,7 Bit2 of X: D += 1 (sprite row)
C $9041,11 Store $8F90 = DE, $8F93 = HL; D += 4
C $904C,5 Store $8F8D = DE
